--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
The standard WebGPU C API header, vendored at wgpu/lib/webgpu.h inside
cogentcore/webgpu and included by cgo when building backend/gpu.

License: BSD 3-Clause.
  Verified from the header's own SPDX identifier, read from the vendored file:

    Copyright 2019-2023 WebGPU-Native developers
